subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: The U.C.L.A. star Tiffany Joh won the United States Women’s Amateur Public Links for the second time in three years, rallying to win four of the last six holes for a 2-and-1 victory in Erin, Wis. She beat Jennifer Song, who is a U.S.C. recruit.
